commit.message:
Fix copyright problems reported by Doug Evans.

* config/frv/cmovc.c, config/frv/cmovh.c, config/frv/cmovw.c,
config/frv/frvbegin.c, config/frv/frvend.c, config/frv/lib1funcs.asm:
Add libgcc exception.

From-SVN: r67672
